the road to wellville is a 1994 american comedy-drama film adaptation of t. coraghessan boyle 's novel of the same name , which tells the story of the doctor and clean-living advocate john harvey kellogg and his methods employed at the battle creek sanitarium at the beginning of the 20th century . the film was written and directed by alan parker . the film stars anthony hopkins as dr. kellogg , matthew broderick as william lightbody , bridget fonda as his spouse eleanor , john cusack as charles ossining , dana carvey as the doctor 's adopted son george , and colm meaney as dr. lionel badger . it was filmed in new paltz , new york at the mohonk mountain house . other locations were the north carolina towns of winnabow and wilmington .